Due to Hespori's [[elemental weakness]] to fire spells, maging Hespori is viable, especially at lower levels and with access to gear that boosts elemental spell damage, such as the [[Harmonised nightmare staff]], [[Twinflame staff]], and [[Smoke battlestaff]] or [[Tome of fire]]. However, meleeing Hespori provides access to [[thralls]] and better special attack weapons, and will typically be cheaper especially if using [[Sunfire runes]] or [[Sunfire pages|pages]].

===Inventory===
*[[Hespori seed]], [[spade]], and, if the bare-handed planting section of [[Barbarian training]] is incomplete, a [[seed dibber]] to harvest and replant Hespori
*[[Knives]] or [[darts]] to quickly kill flowers
*Runes for the best [[fire spell]] you have access to
*A [[prayer potion]] in case of a long fight, or at lower prayer levels
*[[Antipoison]] or 1 dose of [[Super antipoison]]
*The rest any cooked food

